                " Neutron energy range 2.5 to 10.6 MeV.",
                " Sample irradiation time between 2 and 12 hours."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The tritium produced in each sample was",
                " separated in a vacuum apparatus at 1150 C and its",
                " activity determined in an anticoincidence proportional",
                " gas counter. Cross sections were determined relative",
                " to activation monitor reaction cross sections."
              ]
            }
          ],
